Finance-BitPay-API version 0.01
===============================

This module allows object oriented access to the BitPay API calls.
It supports both public and private calls as well
as IPN handling.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

   CGI, JSON, LWP::UserAgent, URI, Data::Dumper

